<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />的店里出售的树苗，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是连在那家<colour id="1" />Nook商店<colour id="65535" />也买不到的，<delay8 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />相当稀有哦～！
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真不愧是<delay8 />植物专家！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />全才虽然也很好，<delay20 />
但专精一项也令人向往呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我听说莳花弄草<delay8 />
可以治愈身心。<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道说<colour id="3" /><delay8 />然然<colour id="65535" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是每天翻弄花土，<delay8 />精神压力为零，<size value="100" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才成就了那样闲适柔和的性情？！<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要不要<delay20 />也去<colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />的店里<delay8 />
买下各种不同的幼苗和种子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />努力培养惹人爱的体质呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道吗？<delay40 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把花种成一排，<delay8 />
不知不觉就会在附近开出新的花，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新开的花有可能是罕见的颜色！
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是<colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />告诉我的，<delay20 />
似乎叫做<delay8 />“杂交育种”。<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要每天浇水就会发生！
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这一定<delay8 />是我们的爱意传达给了花，<delay20 />
所以花用惊喜来回报了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用花作装饰<delay8 />很可爱吧～<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然摘下花朵的瞬间<delay8 />
让人觉得有点可惜<tag a="110" b="0" />
不过，<delay20 /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能够有机会妆点
像我这样时尚的女孩，<delay20 />
花儿一定也如获新生，非常幸福！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道“地球日”吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是大家一起思考<delay8 />自然重要性的日子！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多亏了这个世界上的植物，<delay20 />
我们才能呼吸到新鲜空气，保持健康，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />并且花儿会衬托我<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我今天<delay20 />会抱着<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比以往更深厚的感谢之情，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为花儿们浇水～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>